  <p>
    The Japanese Rail (JR) pass is only available for tourist visitors of Japan.
    It costs ¥208,000 for a 7-day pass and gives you access to most inter-city rail
    systems including the Shinkansen. Just a one-way trip from Tokyo to Hiroshima
    costs ¥18,700 without the pass.
  </p>

