  <p class="break">
    <b>Hiroshima</b><br>
    By the time I arrived to my hostel in Hiroshima it was already night. I
    went to have Okonomiaki at a restaurant nearby and explored the downtown
    area, which was dead quiet, before going to sleep.
  </p>

